text: Ismael Mosqueira (born 1911, date of death unknown) was a Mexican gymnast. He competed in two events at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Mexican male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Mexico Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City
